  "description": "Working with multi-currency Salesforce orgs at the data layer \u2014 `CurrencyIsoCode` field semantics on every object, the `CurrencyType` and `DatedConversionRate` standard objects, the `convertCurrency()` SOQL function, Advanced Currency Management vs basic multi-currency, formula fields with currency conversion, roll-up summaries across currencies, and the irreversibility of enabling multi-currency on an org. NOT for currency UI formatting in LWC (that's Lightning's `lightning-formatted-number`), NOT for tax / financial-doc rounding rules (those are app-layer concerns).",
